{"id":187214,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/美国参议院通过《排华法案》道歉决议/","date":"2011-10-09T05:26:56Z","modified":"2011-10-09T05:26:56Z","title":"美国参议院通过《排华法案》道歉决议","content":"<p>美国参议院一致通过决议就1882年《排华法案》道歉。 《排华法》阻止华人移民到美国，同时禁止当时的美国华人归化美籍。参议院星期四晚间一致通过了这部法案，承认法案违反美国《独立宣言》与宪法的平等原则和精神。主导这项决议案的议员们接下来将推动通过众议院版本的决议案。参议院对当年因这些歧视性立法所造成的错误而受伤害的华人及其后人表示遗憾，并重申承诺保障华人及其他亚裔在美国享有与其他种族完全相同的权益。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/191ed0b5/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%82%E8%AE%AE%E9%99%A2%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E3%80%8A%E6%8E%92%E5%8D%8E%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8B%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E5%86%B3%E8%AE%AE&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F08%2F0522206%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%82%E8%AE%AE%E9%99%A2%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E3%80%8A%E6%8E%92%E5%8D%8E%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8B%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E5%86%B3%E8%AE%AE&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F08%2F0522206%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/115634932435/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/191ed0b5/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/115634932435/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/191ed0b5/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=_0get4Q4mY4:HGsDAxjvQHo:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=_0get4Q4mY4:HGsDAxjvQHo:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WN